name: WTG Status Log
query:
SELECT `tabWTG Status Log`.creation as "Date:Data:200",site_name as "Site:Data:200",customer_name as "Customer Name:Data:200",
`tabWTG Status Log`.wtg_name as "VCB No:Data:200" ,`tabWTG Status Log`.owner as "Attended By(APMS):Data:200" ,
`tabWTG Status Log`.start as "Start:Data:200" ,`tabWTG Status Log`.end as "End:Data:200",
`tabWTG Status Log`.wtg_fault as "Error Code:Data:200" ,`tabWTG Status Log`.status_description as "Status Description:Data:200" ,
`tabWTG Status Log`.root_cause as "Nature Status:Data:200" from `tabWTG Status Log`  Join `tabWTG Master` ON `tabWTG Status Log`.wtg_name= `tabWTG Master`.wtg_name ;
